{"tid":2449194,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[廚具分享] 炭芯濾油壺","createTime":"2021-03-16T12:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T17:34:45.000Z","uid":182683,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"801b685f7fdb67148443098a662efe30b0d07f23","tid":2449194,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YsMLVqM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYsMLVqM.jpg&h=48095bdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次講吓呢個濾油壺 日本好似興左好耐 仲有好多勁靚色簡 不過啲靚色有啲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個用法好簡單 最主係煎炸完野倒入個壺到<br />\n第一層係濾網 隔走啲大粒少少既野 跟住落到中間就係炭咩咩濾芯 去到呢個位會濾好耐 慢慢滴下滴下咁 跟住啲油就會好似新油一樣咁清 連啲味都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以重用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xKPBhEv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxKPBhEv.png&h=25045f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個濾芯佢話可以用20-30次 我經驗係總之啲油濾完望落唔係好清就要換<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲濾芯十幾廿蚊粒好平 不過我係香港都未見過有 要上網買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LVYKryL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLVYKryL.png&h=6e353b09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7TK5Vr9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TK5Vr9.png&h=c71aaeff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全部野都係日本製 抵買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屋企鍾意炸野既要買啦  慳油健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=7bdf1adf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\n食譜就呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYoutube: <a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=3fab4dc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw</a>"},{"pid":"e14224838e31abc511be41f5f73b7b34b26dc4ee","tid":2449194,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T13:10:06.000Z","msg":"啲油就咁室溫放都得<br />\n定要放入雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba90f6f079cea57ca7ee03c31dc9cfc58be00e25","tid":2449194,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e14224838e31abc511be41f5f73b7b34b26dc4ee","tid":2449194,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T13:10:06.000Z","msg":"啲油就咁室溫放都得<br />\n定要放入雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"室溫就得 你當普通油壺咁用就得 之不過有過濾功能"},{"pid":"62f96c2f3a3f39100e196930320dc58a4f099572","tid":2449194,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3377c3e8d6a946c96b8193b6588dac857eb94846","tid":2449194,"uid":45442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:04:50.000Z","msg":"炸一次嘢起碼用500ml油<br />\n呢個壼裝到幾多"},{"pid":"492fee9aabec7d53394be9228f225388a3ae0ab0","tid":2449194,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3377c3e8d6a946c96b8193b6588dac857eb